            <p><a href="https://www.cnet.com/news/twitters-moments-can-now-be-made-by-everyone/" target="_blank">Twitter Moments Can Now be Made by Everyone</a></p>
            <p>Twitter’s Moments feature is now available to all users on the website version of the social network, with mobile anticipated to follow shortly. Every Twitter user can now tell stories through a series of linked tweets, videos, and images. Moments can also be used to track events such as news stories, concerts, and sports in real time.</p>
